  "texts": [
    "It is, then, essential to comprehensively validate the model assumptions and precisely fit the data in question.",
    "This involves pre-processing stages, such as data cleaning, handling missing values, and normalization.",
    "It is also crucial to conduct exploratory data analysis identifying trends, patterns, variable relationships, and outliers.",
    "These steps ensure the reliability and robustness of the results obtained by applying the proposed methodology.",
    "PhaseFitPro ToolThis section introduces PhaseFitPro (PhaseFitPro -Phase-type Fitting Process tool), a tool to automate the evaluation process.We aim to provide a user-friendly interface for those seeking a hassle-free, automatic fitting experience and a more detailed, customizable version for enthusiasts and experts who prefer finer control via manual fitting (Figure 1)."
